item.title: CVE-2022-33313|2024-09-16T19:20:17.687Z -- robustel -- r1510
item.description: Multiple command injection vulnerabilities exist in the web_server action endpoints functionalities of Robustel R1510 3.3.0. A specially-crafted network request can lead to arbitrary command execution. An attacker can send a sequence of requests to trigger these vulnerabilities.The `/action/import_https_cert_file/` API is affected by command injection vulnerability.
